Dependency injection, dependency inversion, construction injection, parameter injection what does it all mean?

DEFINATION
A)Hight level modules should not depend on low level module.Both sould depend on abstraction.
B)abstraction should not depend on details.details should depend on abstraction.


ex-in our code interface is the socket,and that interface should function regardless of the back implementation.We are not intrested in how 
  it's implemented.
  and the purpose of this is to change the implementation of the low level code ex- change the database engin.
